title: Mark Rothko Untitled (Purple, White, and Red)
description:
Magnet developed from Mark Rothko’s Untitled (Purple, White, and Red), 1953, from The Art Institute of Chicago’s collection.

Add some artistic flare to your magnetic surfaces with this masterpiece from our collection.

  • Single Magnet.
  • Dimensions: 2.3 x 2.3 x .25 in.
  • Material: Acrylic
